war.model

Class Seaport

  • java.lang.Object
    • war.model.Seaport

  • @Entity
public class Seaport
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing an Australian seaport. It is related to the NRM region where it is located.
    Since:
    20th Dec. 2012
    Author:
    Guillaume Prevost
